high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room, turn right and walk to the counter with the toaster.
Pick up the closest knife from the front of the counter.
Turn around and carry the knife to the loaf of bread on the counter on the right.
Slice the loaf of bread on the counter.
Turn left and carry the knife to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the knife inside, close the microwave.
Turn right and go to the loaf of bread on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread from the loaf on the counter.
Carry the slice of bread to the microwave to the left.
Open the microwave and put the slice of bread in the microwave, turn on the microwave, after the bread is heated take it out
Turn around carrying the slice of bread, then turn left and bring the bread to the refrigerator.
Put the slice of bread in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated slice of bread in the refrigerator

high_descs: turn left and walk forwards to the near end of the room, then turn right and walk to the kitchen counter to the right of the stove
grab a butterknife off of the kitchen stove
turn around and walk over to the dishwasher on the right side of the room
cut up the loaf of bread on the kitchen counter there
move left a bit and face the microwave on the kitchen counter to the right
place the knife inside of the microwave
move right a bit and face the kitchen counter on the left just before the sink
grab a slice of the loaf of bread off of the counter
turn left and walk to the microwave on your right
place the slice of bread inside of the microwave, cook it, then take it back out
turn around and walk to the fridge on the left side of the room
place the bread slice inside of the fridge
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved slice of bread inside of the fridge

high_descs: Turn left, move forward to the 3rd square away from the counter, turn right, move forward to the counter.
Pick up the knife.
Turn around, move forward to alongside the dishwasher, turn right,
Slice the bread.
Turn left, move forward to the microwave, turn right.
Open the microwave, put the knife inside, close the microwave.
Turn right, move forward to alongside the bread, turn left.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn left, move forward to the microwave, turn right.
Open the microwave door, place the bread inside, close the door, turn on the microwave for 2 seconds, open the door, remove the bread slice.
Turn around, move forward to the counter, turn left, move to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, put the bread on the top shelf, close the fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated slice of bread in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter, left of the toaster.
Pick up the knife that is closest to the edge.
Turn left, move to the counter in front of the bread.
Slice the bread with the knife.
Turn left, move to the counter in front of the microwave.
Place the knife in to the microwave.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the bread.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn left, move to the counter in front of the microwave.
Place the bread slice into the microwave, cook it, then pick it up.
Turn right, move to the refrigerator.
Place the bread slice onto the top shelf of the refrigerator.
Turn to your left and walk across the kitchen, then turn to the counter on your right between the stove and the refrigerator.
Pick up the knife closest to the edge of the counter top.
Turn around and walk past the sink, and turn to your right, in front of the counter top above the dishwasher.
Cut the loaf of bread between the sink and the microwave, on the counter top into slices.
Go to the microwave on the counter to your left.
Place the knife inside the microwave.
Go back to the counter top with the sliced bread to your right.
Remove a slice of bread from the center of the loaf, on the counter top.
Go back to the microwave, to your left.
Place the slice of bread in the microwave, heat it, then remove it from the microwave.
Turn to your left and go to the refrigerator with the slice of bread.
Place the slice of bread in the refrigerator, on the front right corner of the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm slice of bread in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn left and head to the counter with the toaster on it
Grab the knife that is on the counter
Turn around and stop at the counter over the washing machine
Cut the loaf of bread on the counter into slices
Turn left and stop at the microwave
Put the knife in the microwave
Turn right and stop at the counter on the left
Grab a slice of bread off the counter
Turn left and stop at the microwave
Heat the bread in the microwave and then take it out
Turn around and head to the fridge
Put the bread in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Putting a slice of bread in the fridge
